---
export const pagetitle = "Home"; // or any title you want

import Welcome from '../components/Welcome.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout>
    <p class="spaced-paragraph">
        Welcome to your cloud’s personal IT department. Our goal is to “Marie Kondo” your cloud email, drive, and photos.<br />
        <br />
        Do you want to save on paying for more cloud storage?<br />
        <br />
        Do you miss important emails in your cluttered mailbox?<br />
        <br />
        Can’t receive emails or can’t share photos cause you’ve hit your storage limit?<br />
        <br />
        Just plain tired of how messy your cloud email, photos, and drive are?<br />
        <br />
        Got other cloud problems?<br />
        <br />
        Then you’ve come to the right place! We want to help you.
    </p>

    <div class="two-sections">
      <div class="section-link-wrapper">
        <a href="/cleanercloud/Process" class="section-link">
          <section class="left-section">
            <h2>Cleaner Cloud Service</h2>
            <p>Schedule time with one of our IT help desk technicians to create a personalized plan to solve your cloud problems. Meetings with our IT technicians are free of charge, but we ask that we can record our conversation with you.</p>
          </section>
        </a>
        <a href="/cleanercloud/Purchase" class="purchase-btn">Purchase</a>
      </div>
      <div class="section-link-wrapper">
        <a href="/cleanercloud/Process" class="section-link">
          <section class="right-section">
            <h2>Cleaner Cloud Suite</h2>
            <p>Download our AI assisted program to clean up photos, files, and emails in your cloud to save on cloud storage costs. The suite comes with <b>Cleaner Cloud Photos</b>, <b>Cleaner Cloud Drive</b>, and <b>Cleaner Cloud Email</b></p>
          </section>
        </a>
        <a href="/cleanercloud/Purchase" class="purchase-btn">Purchase</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <style>
      .spaced-paragraph {
        line-height: 1.2;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .two-sections {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: stretch;
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1600px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      .section-link-wrapper {
        flex: 1 1 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
      }
      .section-link {
        flex: 1 1 0;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        display: block;
        min-width: 0;
        width: 100%;
      }
      .left-section, .right-section {
        background: #f8f8f8;
        padding: 3rem 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        text-align: center;
        height: 100%;
        transition: box-shadow 0.2s, background 0.2s;
        cursor: pointer;
        position: relative;
      }
      .section-link:hover .left-section,
      .section-link:hover .right-section {
        box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(74,144,226,0.15);
        background: #eaf4fd;
      }
      .purchase-btn {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
        background: #4a90e2;
        color: #fff;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background 0.2s;
        cursor: pointer;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
      }
      .purchase-btn:hover {
        background: #357ab8;
      }
      .left-section h2, .right-section h2 {
        text-align: center;
      }
      @media (max-width: 1000px) {
        .two-sections {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 100vw;
        }
        .section-link-wrapper {
          max-width: 95vw;
        }
        .left-section, .right-section {
          padding: 2rem 1rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
</Layout>
